'''Former vampyres''' are humans that were once [[vampyre juvenile]]s that roamed around [[Meiyerditch]] and have been cured of vampyrism through the combined use of a [[Rod of ivandis|Rod of Ivandis]] or [[Ivandis flail]]'s special attack and a dose of [[Guthix balance]]. Their pale skin colour may be due to the lack of sunlight they received during their days as a vampyre. They reward the player's kindness by giving them a variety of items.

